text: Mönchaltorf is a municipality of the district Uster in the canton of Zurich in Switzerland. ==History== It also holds the record for the longest Apfel Strudel. ==Gallery== File:KircheMönchaltorf.JPG|Church of Mönchaltorf File:Moenchaltorf 125.jpg|Village fountain in frount of Mönchhof File:Moenchaltorf restoracio Muehle 075.jpg|Restaurant Mühle ==References== ==Other websites== * Official Website Category:Municipalities in Uster
